title: Intel Eyes Significantly Lower Valuation in IPO of Mobileye Unit; A target valuation of under $20 billion is expected, down from $50 billion
text:
In another sign of the challenges facing the offering, Mobileye plans to launch its roadshow for prospective investors on Tuesday, a day later than anticipated.

Write to Corrie Driebusch at corrie.driebusch@dowjones.com
